extendedInfo.description: Find DifferencesFive Differences between Two PicturesThis is a very funny game of finding difference.Improve attention skills and exercise brain while playing this completely free arcade game with hundreds of levels.The game has enough HD pictures:Indoor, delicious food, racing car and riotous flowers.Please pay attention to the particulars of each picture, it is not easy to find the differences!Come on, try it out!Game Rules:- There're 5 minor differences between two pictures, you are required to find them by clicking and circling the         differences on each of the picture.- Limited time of 120 seconds.- Each mistake will cost your time.- There're 3 chances of getting help by default. When tip become to 0, you can replay the unlock level to get a tip.Key Words: Find Difference, Find It, Spot the difference, Find Differences, Spot the Differences, let's Spot it, Simply Find it,Scenery, Delicious, Animals, Flowers, Leisure, Entertainment, puzzle game, free, difficultNote:This free software will contain some ads in the notification tray and/or home screen.Some system software misinformation the ads is the virus, please feel at ease to use, Thank you very much for your support!
